rows.label: tlk400908_msg0001
rows.name:
Momomo...! I can read
it! I can read it, mo!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0008
rows.name:
But we have a general
idea of the location...

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0009
rows.name:
For now, we should report
to the Flamebringer.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm going to brag about
how much I helped, mo!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0011
rows.name:
I'll demand a three-year
supply of Tasty Sausages, mo!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0012
rows.name: You're getting a little carried away.

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0013
rows.name:
With that much, Masterpon
could live the rest of his
life without working, mo!

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0014
rows.name:
But isn't it only a
three-year supply...?

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0016
rows.name:
If we go to the palace and speak
to the guards, they'll get us an
audience with Meleph, right?

rows.label: tlk400908_msg0017
rows.name: Yes, that's what she said. Let's go.
